blog.name: smokeinmycoffee
blog.title: BOREDOMCOFFEE
blog.description: An unknown TS fan, HERE TO HAVE FUN, COFFEE AND MEME. To follow her narrative. I'll wait even if it means reading it from her biography 20-30yrs from now. JUST WANT TAY TO BE A FREE GAY.

body:
Call it.. what you mean?

*coffee break*

While having coffee, taylor’s song Call it what you want played in my list and I realized this..

THIS IS A MOCKING SONG!!!!

It’s like:

F*you, since you destroyed what we have we will not share a shit to you.

F*you, I was broken someone fixed me. I’m not drowning anymore. hah! I own this.

F*you, people who used me and the fake me that you keep buying, you can eat that, i don’t give much shit anymore.

F*you, my necklace is none of your concern. I’m wearing it cause of the sentimental value not your validation of whatever sh*t you wanna validate.

F*you, I’m having the time of life with my baby here with me and that’s the fucking TEA!

So yeah.. do whatever makes you sleep at night while I buy wine for tonight’s dinner and we’re cuddling before we sleep.

This is why I think Taylor Swift is one of the biggest genius troll of this decade. I can’t stop to be entertained by all this. At our age, this is how we usually think.

If you don’t agree, I don’t care. share your own realization on your own page. 🖕
